<paragraph id="3E34D799EE14C0773AFEE588806A7131" pageId="21" pageNumber="84">
<normalizedToken id="B278F1A4B3C99B5BA653E360167601A9" originalValue="São">Sao</normalizedToken>
Miguel (Furnas) and Terceira (Monte Brasil), August-September 1930, leg. L. Chopard, det. Benoist (
<bibRefCitation id="2805F79E3AE8C72709A26FF9EA6298F3" author="Benoist, R" journalOrPublisher="Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France" pageId="25" pageNumber="88" pagination="9 - 10" title="Voyage de MM. L. Chopard et A. Mequignon aux Acores (Aout-Septembre 1930)." volume="105" year="1936">Benoist et al. 1936</bibRefCitation>
